I.u[6894] = {n:"Ultra-powerful Combat Bow Meow (GM)",t:18,d:"This super-mighty fighting Bow Meow is the embodiment of super-might. Very impressive. Beware, it can only be entrusted to the care of Game Masters... because they\'re worth it.",ep:1,g:1,l:1,wd:false,fm:false,w:10,c:"PX=3|PX=5",p:1};
I.u[6895] = {n:"Small Combat Bow Meow (GM)",t:18,d:"Less super-mighty than the super-mighty fighting Bow Meow, this small fighting Bow Meow is still very powerful. This pet remains a safe bet for Game Masters but it\'s not the least bit house trained and tends to roll around in its own detritus. Don\'t forget to throw some boiling water over it every once in a while so that it retains its splendour.",ep:1,g:9,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:10,p:1};
I.u[6897] = {n:"Blue Piwi Feather",t:53,d:"This Piwi feather was taken from the butt of a hapless Piwi.",ep:1,g:114,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:10};
I.u[6898] = {n:"Purple Piwi Feather",t:53,d:"This Piwi feather was taken from the butt of a hapless Piwi.",ep:1,g:115,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:10};
I.u[6899] = {n:"Green Piwi Feather",t:53,d:"This Piwi feather was taken from the butt of a hapless Piwi.",ep:1,g:116,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:10};
I.u[6900] = {n:"Red Piwi Feather",t:53,d:"This Piwi feather was taken from the butt of a hapless Piwi.",ep:1,g:117,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:10};
I.u[6902] = {n:"Yellow Piwi Feather",t:53,d:"This Piwi feather was taken from the butt of a hapless Piwi.",ep:1,g:118,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:10};
I.u[6903] = {n:"Pink Piwi Feather",t:53,d:"This Piwi feather was taken from the butt of a hapless Piwi.",ep:1,g:119,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:10};
I.u[6904] = {n:"Used Bwork Protection",t:15,d:"Love can sometimes be more destructive than war, but that\'s not what Bworker told you.",ep:1,g:714,l:200,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,p:1000};
I.u[6905] = {n:"Surprise Bwork Pack",t:89,d:"Opening this pack requires a huge amount of serenity on your part... its contents are sensitive.",ep:1,g:42,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:4,u:true,p:100};
I.u[6906] = {n:"Novice Mercenary",t:14,d:"You will be able to join the Mercenaries using this scroll. The one who receives it will have their name added to the Clan register, as a novice.",ep:1,g:5,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:0,c:"Ps=3&Pa>59",ut:true,p:1};
I.u[6907] = {n:"Neutralizer",t:14,d:"Enables you to set the alignment of the targeted character as Neutral.",ep:1,g:5,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:0,c:"Ps=3&Pa>79",ut:true,p:1};
I.u[6908] = {n:"Boar Belt",t:10,d:"Hairy but elegant, this belt should remind you of your lady-love.",ep:1,g:75,l:18,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:21,p:1050};
I.u[6909] = {n:"Boar Feet",t:11,d:"These are the perfect boots for splashing around in the mud or making big dents in an expensive hardwood floor. It\'s forbidden to wear them on dance floors, beaches and in saunas.",ep:1,g:51,l:22,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:21,p:1525};
I.u[6910] = {n:"Boar Ring",t:9,d:"This ring used to be fixed on the legs of rutting boars so that breeders could easily recognize them. Today, you are the one wearing the ring. You can take from with what you wish...",ep:1,g:73,l:19,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:21,p:1200};
I.u[6911] = {n:"Arachnoring",t:9,d:"This ridiculously small ring will help you overcome your Arachnophobia once and for all.",ep:1,g:76,l:5,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,s:22,p:275};
I.u[6912] = {n:"Arachnobelt",t:10,d:"Made from the rotting remains of decaying Arachnees, you\'ll just love this belt. From time to time, it might come back to life and greedily bite you on the hips. Bloody thing!",ep:1,g:73,l:6,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,s:22,p:305};
I.u[6913] = {n:"Arachelmet",t:16,d:"You\'ll look like a wild Arachnee if you wear this Arachelmet. What will that achieve? Well, you might scare off some flies...",ep:1,g:83,l:6,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:22,p:305};
I.u[6914] = {n:"Arachnee Cutter",t:19,d:"Did you know that Weak Arachnees only have four hairy legs? With only four blows of this axe, you could turn one into an Arachneetrunk. Blimey. Imagine everyone in Amakna doing that. It explains why you don\'t see Weak Arachnees any more, anyway.",ep:1,g:31,l:8,wd:true,fm:true,w:5,an:17,e:[5,4,1,1,50,50,false,false],s:22,p:600};
I.u[6915] = {n:"Mos Kitano",t:9,d:"This is such a light ring that your hands can perform acrobatic feats when it\'s on. It\'s also quite useful if you want to humiliate somebody smaller than you by smashing their head with your thumb.",ep:1,g:71,l:21,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:23,p:1400};
I.u[6916] = {n:"Small Moskito Schoolbag",t:81,d:"Made out of Moskito skin and wings, this bag used to be a big fad in schools. Today, it is old-fashioned and has been replaced by the Small Chief Crocodyl schoolbag. I don\'t get it - one, a Small Chief Crocodyl bag is much more expensive and two, it\'s HORRIBLE. Kids these days.",ep:1,g:59,l:16,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:23,p:900};
I.u[6917] = {n:"Moskabuto",t:16,d:"This headgear takes its name from the eccentric Enutrof who discovered it while stripping a sick old Moskito for all it had. Extremely useful for inexperienced adventurers, this headgear will help you seduce famished Arachnees.",ep:1,g:80,l:15,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:23,p:900};
I.u[6918] = {n:"Moskito Amulet",t:1,d:"This small amulet is not as effective as the famous Arachnamu. It certainly looks good, though... To be worn on a bare, hairy chest for a great jewel-in-the-roughage look.",ep:1,g:75,l:15,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:23,p:800};
I.u[6919] = {n:"Mush Mush Ring",t:9,d:"The Mush Mush has a reputation for being a nasty piece of work. He\'ll pester and bite you at every opportunity, and he\'s very moody. I was married to someone like that once... Smelled like mushrooms too...",ep:1,g:74,l:3,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:24,p:225};
I.u[6920] = {n:"Mush Mush Wedding Ring",t:9,d:"When a Mush Mush gets married, he gives this wedding ring to his bride. Since the bride has no arms, the ring is put delicately on one of its thorns. If you get hold of this ring, you will forever break the sacred bond between the two creatures. At best, the Mush Mush will take you as his bride to make up for it, and just remember, Mush Mushes spend their whole lives where the sun don\'t shine...",ep:1,g:75,l:3,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:24,p:225};
I.u[6921] = {n:"Musheadgear",t:16,d:"Before the prohibition, Musheadgear was smoked or drunk as tea. This headgear really has it all.",ep:1,g:84,l:9,wd:true,fm:true,w:3,s:24,p:425};
I.u[6922] = {n:"Mush Mush Cloak",t:17,d:"The only thing more impressive than a livid Mush Mush is a livid Mush Mush in a cloak. Indeed, this particular cloak is the embodiment of a certain kind of ultra-powerful clothing... pretty ugly clothing if you ask me.",ep:1,g:76,l:9,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:24,p:450};
I.u[6923] = {n:"Lars Amulet",t:1,d:"This amulet used to belong to the great robber \"Thisme\" who was famous for his limitless cruelty and idiotic death. A central figure of Eniripsa folklore, he was crushed and drowned to death in an olive press having just come out of jail after a 30-year sentence for the theft of a giant walnut.",ep:1,g:76,l:16,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:25,p:900};
I.u[6924] = {n:"Robber Daggers",t:5,d:"These sharp daggers are very popular among robbers and very unpopular among the elderly for one and the same reason. The daggers cast spells that let them steal Kamas from adversaries. At least that\'s the story their victims tell.",ep:1,g:9,l:12,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,an:13,e:[5,3,1,1,30,50,false,false],s:25,p:600};
I.u[6925] = {n:"Robber Belt",t:10,d:"This beautiful belt is essential you if you ever decide to become a highwayman. Don\'t wear it round town, though, you\'ll be arrested on sight.",ep:1,g:72,l:15,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:25,p:850};
I.u[6926] = {n:"Prespwig",t:16,d:"With this prespwig on, you\'ll look like Debbie Crockett, the most celebrated huntress of the modern age, but a tragic victim of premature baldness. That\'s not to say that this rat-bitten, off-red wig is any better than a balding nut.",ep:1,g:81,l:36,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:31,p:3600};
I.u[6927] = {n:"Prespic Cloak",t:17,d:"This reddish small cloak can be also used as a rug or doormat so that you can redecorate the house on the cheap.",ep:1,g:75,l:37,wd:true,fm:true,w:3,s:31,p:3800};
I.u[6928] = {n:"Prespic Ring",t:9,d:"This ring, both simple and original, will seduce adventurers who long for the good things in life but could never afford them. The kind who would beat the daylights out of helpless animals and strip them of anything resembling an ornament. There\'s no shortage of them, believe me.",ep:1,g:72,l:38,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,s:31,p:4000};
I.u[6929] = {n:"Prespic Belt",t:10,d:"The Prespic Belt is the ideal belt for keeping your hips warm. It itches like hell, though... you wanna be hard to wear this one!",ep:1,g:71,l:33,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:31,p:3000};
I.u[6930] = {n:"Crackler Helmet",t:16,d:"This helmet directly hewed in stone is worth its weight in gold. It will both protect you from the attacks of a Crackrock and allow you to give head butts worthy of that of Desirock. It\'s perfect to make your opponents go off their rocker.",ep:5,g:85,l:44,wd:true,fm:true,w:200,s:26,p:5300};
I.u[6931] = {n:"Crackler Cloak",t:17,d:"This stone cloak is a bit too stiff, but you\'ll be grateful when you\'re in danger of being spat on by a Crackler.",ep:5,g:77,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,s:26,p:5800};
I.u[6933] = {n:"Crackler Boots",t:11,d:"Incredibly heavy but equally effective, these rocky boots will give you a good excuse to drag your feet when you have to defend a Perceptor in a fight you know you can\'t win.",ep:5,g:52,l:47,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,s:26,p:4700};
I.u[6934] = {n:"Crackler Amulet",t:1,d:"This amulet is as heavy as a bulimic Blop. It has not been designed for weak adventurers. However, once you get used to bearing its heavy weight around your neck, you\'ll sure cut a dash!",ep:5,g:77,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,s:26,p:4600};
I.u[6935] = {n:"Crackler Belt",t:10,d:"Wear it on your waist and you\'ll gain the respect of your peers. Wear it on your head and you\'ll be the laughing stock of Astrub",ep:5,g:74,l:45,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,s:26,p:5400};
I.u[6936] = {n:"Green Scara Helmet",t:16,d:"With this helmet on, you\'ll be able to pretend to be a Scaraleaf hunter.",ep:3,g:78,l:44,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:27,p:5200};
I.u[6937] = {n:"Red Scara Helmet",t:16,d:"Your friends will think that you\'ve joined the elite Scaraleaf hunter clan if you wear this helmet.",ep:3,g:77,l:44,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:28,p:5200};
I.u[6938] = {n:"White Scara Helmet",t:16,d:"Your friends will think that you\'ve joined the elite Scaraleaf hunter clan if you wear this helmet.",ep:3,g:79,l:44,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:29,p:5200};
I.u[6939] = {n:"Blue Scara Helmet",t:16,d:"With this helmet on, your friends will think that you\'ve joined the elite Scaraleaf hunter clan.",ep:3,g:76,l:44,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:30,p:5200};
I.u[6940] = {n:"Green Scaracape",t:17,d:"Have you ever dreamt of wearing a cape made of Scaraleaf shells? Well, here\'s your chance! Once equipped, you should feel as if you were a real Scaraleaf and you might even succeed to slide and skid around. This should be enough to take aback a whole herd of Trools.",ep:3,g:74,l:45,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:27,p:5500};
I.u[6941] = {n:"Blue Scaracape",t:17,d:"Who\'s never dreamt of wearing a cloak made of Scareleaf shells? Once equipped, you\'ll probably believe yourself to be a true Scaraleaf, and maybe you\'ll manage to move on by way of slipping and skidding. That\'s enough to take a crowd of Trools aback.",ep:3,g:73,l:45,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:30,p:5500};
I.u[6942] = {n:"Red Scaracape",t:17,d:"Who\'s never dreamt of wearing a cloak made of Scareleaf shells? Once equipped, you\'ll probably believe yourself to be a true Scaraleaf, and maybe you\'ll manage to move along by way of slipping and skidding. That\'s enough to take a crowd of Trools aback.",ep:3,g:72,l:45,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:28,p:5500};
I.u[6943] = {n:"White Scaracape",t:17,d:"Who\'s never dreamt of wearing a cloak made of Scareleaf shells? Once equipped, you\'ll probably believe yourself to be a true Scaraleaf, and maybe you\'ll manage to move along by way of slipping and skidding. That\'s enough to take a crowd of Trools aback.",ep:3,g:71,l:45,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:29,p:5500};
I.u[6944] = {n:"Green Scararing",t:9,d:"When you\'ll wear this ring, you\'ll spare a thought for all the Scaraleaves you have wiped out. You then maybe ask yourself if it is worth this slaughter... Yeah, of course it is worth it!",ep:3,g:69,l:43,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:27,p:5000};
I.u[6945] = {n:"Red Scararing",t:9,d:"When you\'ll wear this ring, you\'ll spare a thought for all the Scaraleaves you have wiped out. You then maybe ask yourself if it is worth this slaughter... Yeah, of course it is worth it!",ep:3,g:68,l:43,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:28,p:5000};
I.u[6946] = {n:"White Scararing",t:9,d:"When you\'ll wear this ring, you\'ll spare a thought for all the Scaraleaves you have wiped out. You then maybe ask yourself if it is worth this slaughter... Yeah, of course it is worth it!",ep:3,g:67,l:43,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:29,p:5000};
I.u[6947] = {n:"Blue Scararing",t:9,d:"When you\'ll wear this ring, you\'ll spare a thought for all the Scaraleaves you have wiped out. You then maybe ask yourself if it is worth this slaughter... Yeah, of course it is worth it!",ep:3,g:70,l:43,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:30,p:5000};
I.u[6948] = {n:"Green Scarabelt",t:10,d:"The Scarabelt was worn as an indicator of a warrior\'s fist-fighting skills. With a Green Scarabelt, your enemy knew you were a beginner. A red one meant that you were a lusty warrior who ate the uncooked internal organs of your enemies just for fun... And the white one indicated that you were really tough. A blue one meant you didn\'t spend long enough saving up for one of the others.",ep:3,g:67,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:27,p:5600};
I.u[6949] = {n:"White Scarabelt",t:10,d:"The Scarabelt was worn as an indicator of a warrior\'s fist-fighting skills. With a Green Scarabelt, your enemy knew you were a beginner. A red one meant that you were a lusty warrior who ate the uncooked internal organs of your enemies just for fun... And the white one indicated that you were really tough. A blue one meant you didn\'t spend long enough saving up for one of the others.",ep:3,g:69,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:29,p:5600};
I.u[6950] = {n:"Red Scarabelt",t:10,d:"The Scarabelt was worn as an indicator of a warrior\'s fist-fighting skills. With a Green Scarabelt, your enemy knew you were a beginner. A red one meant that you were a lusty warrior who ate the uncooked internal organs of your enemies just for fun... And the white one indicated that you were really tough. A blue one meant you didn\'t spend long enough saving up for one of the others.",ep:3,g:68,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:28,p:5600};
I.u[6951] = {n:"Blue Scarabelt",t:10,d:"The Scarabelt was worn as an indicator of a warrior\'s fist-fighting skills. With a Green Scarabelt, your enemy knew you were a beginner. A red one meant that you were a lusty warrior who ate the uncooked internal organs of your enemies just for fun... And the white one indicated that you were really tough. A blue one meant you didn\'t spend long enough saving up for one of the others.",ep:3,g:70,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:30,p:5600};
I.u[6952] = {n:"Boowolf Headgear",t:16,d:"The smell coming from this Boowolf Headgear will handily mask your terrible breath.",ep:1,g:131,l:61,wd:true,fm:true,w:4,s:32,p:10000};
I.u[6953] = {n:"Boowolf Boots",t:11,d:"These boots are coated with Boowolf hair. They are extremely useful for cleaning dusty wooden floors or fixing up the heads of your enemies as they lie dead on the battle field.",ep:1,g:76,l:61,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:32,p:9700};
I.u[6954] = {n:"Boowolf Cloak",t:17,d:"This Boowolf fur makes for excellent protection against the cold... and also adventurers with a highly developed sense of smell.",ep:1,g:99,l:64,wd:true,fm:true,w:5,s:32,p:11000};
I.u[6955] = {n:"Boowolf Thong",t:10,d:"Used as a whip, this thong can be a lot more efficient than it looks to motivate your fellow travellers when they\'ve lost the will to live.",ep:1,g:92,l:49,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:32,p:6500};
I.u[6956] = {n:"Boowolf Ring",t:9,d:"Beware! This ring will make your finger stink. Although this foul smell may cover a worse smell... This may be the best thing that could happen to your finger... and your hands in general in fact.",ep:1,g:103,l:51,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:32,p:7000};
I.u[6957] = {n:"Crackler Blade",t:6,d:"This sword used to cut the granite blocks for the city walls of Bonta and Brakmar. Nowadays, it\'s used to crush creatures in battle.",ep:5,g:54,l:37,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,an:14,tw:true,e:[5,6,1,1,50,50,false,true],s:26,p:3800};
I.u[6958] = {n:"Brilliant Hermiturtlook",t:16,d:"Eternally fashionable, this hat will give you a unique look - a long, discreet look up the skirts of the Cra women. Perfect for those warm summer night parties.",ep:5,g:82,l:22,wd:true,fm:true,w:12,p:1525};
I.u[6961] = {n:"Gangster Ring",t:9,d:"This ring is as popular with dentists as it is with gangsters. They both use it to  break the teeth of careless people... They both use similar drills too, but let\'s not dwell on that...",ep:1,g:77,l:17,wd:true,fm:true,w:2,s:25,p:1000};
I.u[6962] = {n:"Dofusian Present",t:89,d:"We won\'t spoil the surprise and tell you what\'s inside! Just have fun my friend and don\'t party too much!",ep:1,g:42,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:1,u:true,p:1};
I.u[6963] = {n:"Minotoball\'s Balls",t:12,d:"These incredibly big balls are delicious. You\'ll think there\'s no end to them, but isn\'t that a good thing?",ep:1,g:143,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:1,u:true,p:1};
I.u[6964] = {n:"Brakmarian Intercity-Express Potion",t:12,d:"This rice-based potion enables Brakmarians to return to their hometown instantaneously.",ep:1,g:145,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,c:"Ps=2|Ps=0|Ps=3",u:true,p:1};
I.u[6965] = {n:"Bontarian Intercity-Express Potion",t:12,d:"This rice-based potion enables Bontarians to return to their hometown instantaneously.",ep:1,g:144,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,c:"Ps=1|Ps=0|Ps=3",u:true,p:1};
I.u[6966] = {n:"Class Spell Scroll: Jinx",t:75,d:"(Double click to learn the spell)\nThis scroll will teach Srams the class spell \'Jinx\'.",ep:1,g:14,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:1,c:"PG=4",u:true,p:10000};
I.u[6967] = {n:"Apprentice Mercenary Induction Scroll",t:14,d:"Use this parchment to promote a Mercenary to Apprentice.",ep:1,g:5,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:0,c:"Ps=3&Pa>59",ut:true,p:1};
I.u[6968] = {n:"Mercenary Induction Scroll",t:14,d:"With this parchment, an apprentice Mercenary can be promoted to Mercenary.",ep:1,g:5,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:0,c:"Ps=3&Pa>79",ut:true,p:1};
I.u[6969] = {n:"Great Mercenary Induction Scroll",t:14,d:"With this parchment, a Mercenary can be promoted to Great Mercenary.",ep:1,g:5,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:0,c:"Ps=3&Pa>79",ut:true,p:1};
I.u[6970] = {n:"Master Mercenary Induction Scroll",t:14,d:"With this parchment, a Mercenary can be promoted to Master Mercenary.",ep:1,g:5,l:1,wd:true,fm:true,w:0,c:"Ps=3&Pa>79",ut:true,p:1};
I.u[6971] = {n:"Mercenary Disciple\'s Clint",t:16,d:"This hat is quite a good replica of the famous Clint. It will perfectly suit mercenary disciples who are convinced they are master material.",ep:1,g:38,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:20,c:"Ps=3",p:1};
I.u[6975] = {n:"Novice Mercenary\'s Clint",t:16,d:"This ultra-powerful hat is the Mercenary emblem. It has the power to protect you from both the rain and the sun... a good start at least.",ep:1,g:38,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:20,p:1};
I.u[6978] = {n:"Peki",t:18,d:"From a distance, this creature looks just like a Bow Wow. A simple glance at its head and you can see it\'s been through terrible trials... which eventually led it to become a vegetarian and to subscribe for life to the Pet Sanctuary Foundation. As such, it will only eat vegetables and plants that grow on Pandala island.",ep:3,g:12,l:60,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,c:"PZ=1",p:1};
I.u[6980] = {n:"Vulbis Dofus",t:23,d:"This Dofus was laid by a dragon which decided to remain anonymous. Even the wisest adventurers still wonder why.",ep:11,g:4,l:6,wd:false,fm:true,w:1,p:500000};
I.u[6981] = {n:"Ice Daggers",t:5,d:"The blade of these daggers is made of ice. Reminds me of an old incident that had the detectives working overtime... A fella called Tum Sellick stabbed his buddy with one of these things over a couple of Kamas... Nice crime... They found the novelty ice-cube maker in his house though... NICKED!",ep:19,g:44,l:150,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,an:13,tw:true,e:[10,3,1,1,30,50,false,false],c:"CA>250&CS>150",p:15};
I.u[6982] = {n:"Dagg\'Onies",t:5,d:"These daggers are soaked in the blood of various evil creatures, such as children. They are very special.",ep:18,g:50,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:15,an:13,e:[10,3,1,1,30,50,false,false],c:"CA>60",p:5775};
I.u[6983] = {n:"Dagg\'Ressif",t:5,d:"Only sharpened once every ten years, these daggers retain their lethal edge because of the dark magic that possesses them. They can sometimes be seen walking the streets at the weekend, playing loud music and staring threateningly at passersby.",ep:19,g:47,l:143,wd:true,fm:true,w:15,an:13,tw:true,e:[10,3,1,1,30,50,false,false],c:"CS>250&CA>100",p:15};
I.u[6984] = {n:"Gobbly Killer Apprentice Daggers",t:5,d:"These daggers belonged to a Sadida whose dazzling ascent will be remembered forever in Amaknan history. From a young age, this Sadida dedicated his humble life to Gobbly hunting... the villagers found it hilarious... word spread and soon folk came from all around to watch him hunt those ridiculous balls of wool. His revenge was terrible and long-lived. When the price of Gobbly skins skyrocketed, he became so rich that he paid to have every last villager who mocked him hunted down and murdered. He\'s storing their skins too, but the stock market isn\'t going his way.",ep:18,g:46,l:113,wd:true,fm:true,w:15,an:13,tw:true,e:[5,3,1,1,25,50,false,false],c:"CS>300&CA>100",p:32750};
I.u[6986] = {n:"Broken Mount Stinkky Shield",t:82,d:"This shield has seen a few battles too many, in this state it is good for nothing. Perhaps Bouwada, in Pandala village, could replace it for you.",ep:18,g:1,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:20,c:"BI=non équipable",p:5400};
I.u[6987] = {n:"Risky Soul Stone for Small Souls",t:83,d:"You\'ll have a limited chance of capturing level 50 souls using this soul stone.",ep:5,g:1,l:1,wd:false,fm:true,w:1,tw:true,p:1250};
I.u[6988] = {n:"Sulik",t:16,d:"The sister of a wild Xelor who was kidnapped by unscrupulous slave drivers used to wear this thing for her nightly shows, the nature of which I will not repeat here.",ep:19,g:92,l:172,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,p:56100};
I.u[6989] = {n:"Nee Cap",t:16,d:"This hat was made a long time ago by apprentice tailors who wanted to protect themselves from the violent fits of rage of Mirko, their boss. This fine business man was often forced to kick his apprentices in the head when they didn\'t work fast enough. From what I\'ve heard, that was far too good for the lazy bast...",ep:19,g:86,l:120,wd:true,fm:true,w:20,p:37025};
I.u[6990] = {n:"Mothat",t:16,d:"This hat is a tribute to the distant cousins of the Moskitoes: the Moths. A lot bigger and a lot kinder than the Moskitoes, the Moths took such good care of their livestock that they soon became extinct from self-inflicted famine. From this tragic story, we have the common insult \'Moth\' as in, \'Poor bloody Moth\', which describes a fellow who discovers his spouse is devastatingly gluttonous...",ep:19,g:87,l:113,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,p:32925};
I.u[6991] = {n:"Guavhat",t:16,d:"This strange-looking hat looks like a big dehydrated rotting fruit... A bit like you after a night out at the pub.",ep:18,g:88,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,p:5800};
I.u[6992] = {n:"Kannipiwi",t:16,d:"An improved version of the famous Kanniball mask, the Kannipiwi will make you look like a real Piwi hunter to your friends.",ep:12,g:89,l:55,wd:true,fm:true,w:5,p:8000};
I.u[6993] = {n:"Hallelujah Cloak",t:17,d:"Lonard Kohen, the famous minstrel with the voice of a castrated Crackler (which is still incredibly low) was burnt alive in front of the bank of Bonta after causing a moral scandal with his latest, and last, song \"Tower of Thong\". A full recording was made of his cries of agony, which he had the vision to frame in C#m, modulate to Fb, and resolve in a risqué but manageable G#. Niiice.",ep:18,g:79,l:46,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,p:5600};
I.u[6994] = {n:"Hooded Cloak",t:17,d:"This hood-cloak hybrid is just amazing. If it was made of leather, Captain Chafer would have loved it.",ep:1,g:80,l:58,wd:true,fm:true,w:10,p:8875};
